PART 7: THE TAU-360 RESONANCE
======================================================================
  The tau^3 tower:
    (tau^3)^0 = tau^ 0 =       1.0000  (â‰ˆ 6.222^0 =       1.0000)
    (tau^3)^1 = tau^ 3 =       6.2223  (â‰ˆ 6.222^1 =       6.2223)
    (tau^3)^2 = tau^ 6 =      38.7166  (â‰ˆ 6.222^2 =      38.7170)
    (tau^3)^3 = tau^ 9 =     240.9045  (â‰ˆ 6.222^3 =     240.9089)
    (tau^3)^4 = tau^12 =    1498.9713  (â‰ˆ 6.222^4 =    1499.0074)
    (tau^3)^5 = tau^15 =    9326.9930  (â‰ˆ 6.222^5 =    9327.2739)

  tau^0 = 1       (ground state)
  tau^3 â‰ˆ 6.222   (â‰ˆ period 6)
  tau^6 â‰ˆ 38.72   (â‰ˆ 6^2 = 36)
  tau^9 â‰ˆ 240.9   (â‰ˆ 6^3 = 216)
  tau^12 â‰ˆ 1498.9 (â‰ˆ 6^4 = 1296)

  Each TRIPLE of tau powers â‰ˆ one power of 6.
  But with increasing overshoot (because tau^3 > 6).

  Now: 360/tau^9 = 1.494368
  This is close to 360/240.9 â‰ˆ 1.494 â‰ˆ 3/2 = the perfect fifth!

  360/tau^9 = 1.4943678290
  3/2 = 1.5000000000

  360/tau^9 â‰ˆ 3/2!!! The ratio is ALMOST exactly 3/2!

  Difference: -0.0056321710

  So: 360 â‰ˆ (3/2) * tau^9 = (3/2) * (tau^3)^3.

  Since tau^3 â‰ˆ 6.222:
  360 â‰ˆ (3/2) * 6.222^3 = (3/2) * 240.9 â‰ˆ 361.4.
  Close but not exact (because tau^3 â‰  6 exactly).

  If tau^3 WERE exactly 6:
  (3/2) * 6^3 = (3/2) * 216 = 324. Not 360.

  But (5/3) * 6^3 = (5/3) * 216 = 360. EXACT!

  So 360 = (5/3) * 6^3 = interaction/cycle * period^3.

  AND: 360/tau^9 â‰ˆ 3/2, but the EXACT expression is:
  360 = (5/3) * 6^3 (using integer period 6)
  360 â‰ˆ (3/2) * tau^9 (using continuous period tau^3)

  The BRIDGE between these:
  5/3 (rational, exact) â†” 3/2 (approximate in tau)
  Both are superparticular ratios (of the form (n+1)/n).
  5/3 = the major sixth in music.
  3/2 = the perfect fifth in music.
  
  VERIFICATIONS:
  360 = (5/3)*6^3 = (5/3)*216 = 360
  360/tau^9 = 1.4943678290
